{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"560961f44a","title":"北京市军事管制委员会负责人谈取缔一切反动组织","origin":"1967年2月27日《红卫兵报》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e0c801bf63","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":25,"articleId":"560961f44a"}],"tags":[{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"54c660ae56","name":"上山下乡","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"fd183a834c","name":"北京市军管会负责人"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ab72bffacb","type":"title","text":"北京市军事管制委员会负责人谈取缔一切反动组织","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"af20d297d8","type":"authors","text":"北京市军管会负责人","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"4435138c42","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央，国务院2·12号通知第二条（对组织采取的办法）有九个组织不是好组织，应该宣布取缔，有三个反动组织。不是好组织嘛，就是坏组织，反动的有三个。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"16d5ac4eb0","type":"paragraph","text":"1．全国灭资军造反团总部。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"4199a9525e","type":"paragraph","text":"2．全国国营农场红色造反兵团。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"a28d58400a","type":"paragraph","text":"3．全国上山下乡知识青年捍卫真理革命造反团。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"f410a3966c","type":"paragraph","text":"4．全国军垦战士革命造反团。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"71bc77c606","type":"paragraph","text":"5．国际红卫军中国支队。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"816bb5824b","type":"paragraph","text":"6．全国红色劳动者造反总团，简称“全红总”。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"c56ed38310","type":"paragraph","text":"7．全国上山下乡知识青年红色革命造反团。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"e2b9de13a9","type":"paragraph","text":"8．全国上山下乡知识青年红色第一线战斗队。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"a865f34788","type":"paragraph","text":"9．全国聋人革命造反联络总部。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"57ce6be0c7","type":"paragraph","text":"第一个，第二个，第六个，这是三个反动组织。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"02ec4607ef","type":"paragraph","text":"从他们成立以来，在北京活动的共同特点有以下几点：","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"61d8a79bef","type":"paragraph","text":"1．组织本身就是坏的，是坏人组成的，是社会渣滓组成的，地、富、反、坏、右；流氓、临时工、合同工中的一些渣滓。总的来说就是坏人。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"2dd8b9ac78","type":"paragraph","text":"2．破坏文化大革命，矛头指向中央文革，指向毛主席。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"4fcbf83f42","type":"paragraph","text":"3．大搞经济主义。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"9419706382","type":"paragraph","text":"4．挑动群众搞武斗。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"bfae08921e","type":"paragraph","text":"5．抢劫、霸占。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"4f40e86ec3","type":"paragraph","text":"6．伙同一些坏人冲中南海。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"0077d0b583","type":"paragraph","text":"7．严重破坏国家财产。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"ece2a1f7ae","type":"paragraph","text":"8．乱搞男女关系、强奸、甚至轮奸。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"54b961419c","type":"paragraph","text":"三个反动组织的主要事情，一个一个地介绍如下：","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"a9838ab169","type":"paragraph","text":"1．全国灭资军造反团总部。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"c41eabc56e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）是坏人组成的，地、富、反、坏、右。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"5a3fd6211b","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）长权霸占国家房子。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"00408ebadc","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）伙同坏人冲中南海。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"82d2eaa9b5","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）大搞经济主义。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"0ec6fd1394","type":"paragraph","text":"2．全国国营农场红色造反兵团。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"7a58862405","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）公开集会反对《人民日报》“抓革命，促生产”的宣传。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"7e85fd0b50","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）与劳改犯一起冲中南海。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"ec4ea27670","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）奸污妇女。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"e65f21a405","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）大搞经济主义。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"2859e2b551","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）严重破坏国家财产。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"05e60367c6","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）挑动武斗。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"35dd1a2787","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“全红总”，头头是王振海。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"f58227c6c6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）它的组成是临时工、合同工里面的坏人，它到处造谣撞骗，说中央承认自己了。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"2bb05d7f70","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）煽动一些人到北京市胡闹，在全国各地招来一些人到北京取闹。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"d4122418b5","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）大搞经济主义。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"39cd96caf9","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）冲国务院接待站，绑架工作人员。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"c8aee88dba","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）积极为五类分子翻案。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"04ee74b98b","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）以中央名义发通告，发到全国；私自与外国人开座谈会，大肆诬蔑社会主义制度。他们的后台据说是国民党少将。根据调查他们昨天晚上还在开会。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"42028eedc9","type":"paragraph","text":"（以上是传达记录）","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"bb3dca90e5","type":"paragraph","text":"谁反对毛主席就打倒谁！谁反对中央文革谁就是反革命！","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"b5f54ce8dd","type":"paragraph","text":"用鲜血和生命保卫毛主席、保卫中央文革！","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"d085b1857e","type":"paragraph","text":"誓死和中央文革战斗在一起，胜利在一起！","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"3eb94d9f4a","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒全国灭资军造反团总部！","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"d42786a3f2","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒全国国营农场红色造反兵团！","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"a73854f245","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒全国红色劳动者造反总团！","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"3104e511b0","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒一切反革命组织！","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"862970c013","type":"paragraph","text":"敌人不投降，就叫他灭亡！","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"0590293dae","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政万岁！","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"f09dc6198d","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的中国共产党万岁！","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"1204b8a6d0","type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的导师，伟大的领袖、伟大的统帅、伟大的舵手毛主席万岁！万岁！万万、岁！","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"},{"id":"3c5588f6c9","type":"paragraph","text":" 中国科学院红卫兵革命造反司令部1967年2月25日印","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a"}],"page":{"id":"d4ba8cf322","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"560961f44a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}